OL,7,FA BBC reporter has been criticised for
OL,8,Fhis line of questioning during a Bafta
OL,9,Finterview with All Of Us Strangers
OL,10,Factor, Andrew Scott.
OL,12,FColin Paterson interviewed the star on
OL,13,Fthe red carpet during the BBC's
OL,14,Fcoverage of the 2024 Baftas, for which
OL,15,FAll Of Us Strangers was nominated for
OL,16,FOutstanding British Film.
