OL,3,CBBC reporter criticised for
OL,4,C'disgusting' Bafta interview with
OL,5,CAndrew Scott
OL,7,FAsking the actor about another Bafta-
OL,8,Fnominated film, Saltburn, Paterson
OL,9,Finitially asked Scott if he knew
OL,10,Ffellow Irish actor Barry Keoghan, who
OL,11,Ftook the lead role.
OL,13,FHe then moved on to ask Scott for his
OL,14,Freaction to "when (he) first saw the
OL,15,Fnaked dance scene" at the end of
OL,16,FSaltburn, with Scott replying that he
OL,17,F"won't spoil it for anybody."
