OL,3,CBBC reporter criticised for
OL,4,C'disgusting' Bafta interview with
OL,5,CAndrew Scott
OL,7,FHowever, Paterson then asked the
OL,8,Factor: "There is a lot of talk about
OL,9,Fprosthetics - how well do you know
OL,10,Fhim?"
OL,12,FScott then walks away from the
OL,13,Finterview, saying, "See you guys," as
OL,14,FPaterson says, "Too much, too much."
OL,16,FThe question from the BBC reporter has
OL,17,Fbeen met with criticism on X, formerly
OL,18,Fknown as Twitter.
