OL,7,FOne user posted a clip of the
OL,8,Finterview, writing: "This is frankly
OL,9,Fdisgusting. Andrew Scott is there to
OL,10,Fsupport his multiple nominated film
OL,11,Fand this is what you ask? Then when he
OL,12,Flooks visibly uncomfortable the guy
OL,13,Fcarried on. Truly horrid."
